race.comment: MAGNATEAR (1) returns from a let-up and can surprise some of his more fancied rivals over the 1200m. Should take control early with Stanley's 3kg claim and will prove hard to get past in what looks a winnable race. DOLLAR MAGIC (9) near her top for this third-up and can stalk MAGNATEAR out to the 1200m. Chipped away late when a courageous third to King's Secret over 1100m at this track. Yet to win at this track and she won't get a better chance today. CIGAR FLICK (3) unsuited first-up with an eye-catching fourth over 1100m at this track. Yet to win second-up and stays in the mix with the claim. GOODLUCKTOME (4) sharp on his day and has a handy fresh record with Rawiller engaged. Given the two soft trials and has the ratings to take this out. SEMILLION (5) resumes after disappointing last prep but looks to have come back well after impressing in his two trials. Will go forward and be ridden for luck.
